de.learnlib.algorithms.features.observationtable.reader

Class SimpleObservationTable<I,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.learnlib.algorithms.features.observationtable.reader.SimpleObservationTable<I,D>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - The input type.
    D - The output domain type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObservationTable<I,D>

    public class SimpleObservationTable<I,D>
extends Object
implements ObservationTable<I,D>
    This class represents the data structure of an ObservationTable wihout providing any meaningful functionalily. It is used to store the result of reading string representations like with OTUtils.fromString(String, net.automatalib.words.Alphabet, ObservationTableReader).
